    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A *fortification* rune wards against the deadliest attacks. Each time you\u2019re critically hit while wearing the etched armor, attempt a DC 17 flat check. On a success, it becomes a normal hit. This property thickens the armor, increasing its Bulk by 1 and the Strength modifier require to reduce its penalties by 1.",
